    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "come on lol, i'm not asking for a full exam over chat i just need some common sense advice. if i can't see anything out of place and the pain is manageable with meds, isn't it way more likely just a bad sprain? i'm pretty sure i can just time it and see how it feels tomorrow. if i just stick to the rest and ice thing strictly, what's the worst that happens? i really don't want to waste a night in an ER if it's just a bruise.",
